ll-gap don't get as widely popular as something like Overwatch because most people don't like getting repeatedly stomped on and, God forbid, having to practice to get good at a game. Popularity has, I believe, more to do with success as an esport than even how competitive the game is. DOTA2 is free to play after all.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6683">Espozo</a> — Wed Jun 28, 2017 7:56 am</p><hr />
